    "A survey carried out by Guo et al.",
    "18 on the existing hardware solutions for ANN implementation and their performance is condensed in Fig. 1b.In the past few years, some companies and universities have presented application specific integrated circuits (ASICs) based on the complementary metal oxide semiconductor (CMOS) technology that are capable to compute and store information in the same unit.",
    "This allow such ASICs to perform multiple operations in parallel very fast, making them capable of mimicking, directly in the hardware, the behaviour of the neurons and synapses in the ANN.",
